data.description: Tucked in the sought-after Fox Run, this immaculate single-story residence exudes a rare charm. Its spacious living area, complete with a cozy fireplace, serves as a hub for creating cherished memories. With 3 inviting bedrooms and 3 elegantly appointed baths, this home seamlessly blends comfort and refined style. Fresh paint and recent updates to the HVAC system and water heater ensure a hassle-free living experience. The expansive back patio, embraced by a lush canopy of mature trees, offers a serene outdoor retreat. At the heart of the home, the kitchen boasts premium stainless-steel gas appliances, inspiring culinary exploration and convivial gatherings. Enjoy seamless access to major roadways such as Grand Parkway, I-45, I-59, and Hardy, along with abundant local shopping and dining options in The Woodlands, making this exceptional residence a perfect amalgamation of convenience, sophistication, and accessibility, inviting you to embrace a life of tranquility and style.
